Creating data
========================================================

```{r dataCreation1, exercise=TRUE}
a=c("Public", "Private", "Other")
b=c(200, 20, 80)
inventedDF = data.frame(Type=a,
                        Count=b)
inventedDF

```


Prepating ggplot2
========================================================



```{r baseGGplot, exercise=TRUE}
a=c("Public", "Private", "Other")
b=c(200, 20, 80)
inventedDF = data.frame(Type=a,
                        Count=b)
####

library(ggplot2)

base=ggplot(data=inventedDF, 
            aes(x=Type,
                y=Count))
```

