Default plus Title
========================================================
class:medium-code

```{r barsTitle, exercise=TRUE}
# all text for titles
Titles=list(Ti="Nice title",
            STi="sub is here",
            XTi="Type of school",
            YTi="Amount of schools",
            Sou="Source: imaginary")

####
library(ggplot2)
base=ggplot(data=inventedDF,
            aes(x=Type,y=Count))

bar1= base + geom_bar(stat = 'identity')
#
# using texts
bar1= bar1 + labs(title = Titles$Ti,
                  subtitle = Titles$STi,
                  xlab=Titles$XTi,
                  ylab=Titles$YTi,
                  caption = Titles$Sou)
```

****
```{r}
bar1
```

